sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine provided with a water tank,  A rotating cage is arranged inside the water tank,  The edge portion of the rotary cage is made by bending the metal plate into a cylindrical shape,  Wherein such a washing machine is manufactured by performing a coating step in which an antifouling coating having an antifouling function is applied on a surface of a plate forming an outer surface of a rotating cage edge portion,  and a washing machine having an antifouling coating is applied on the outer surface of the rotating cage edge portion.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种设置有水箱的洗衣机，在这个水箱的内部设置有旋转笼， 旋转保持架的边缘部分是将金属板弯曲成圆筒形制造的，其中这种洗衣机的制造是执行涂覆步骤，其中具有防污功能的防污涂料涂覆在形成旋转保持架边缘部分外表面的板的表面，具有防污涂料的洗衣机涂覆在旋转保持架边缘部分外表面。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine,  Wherein the first water circulation path and the second water circulation path are arranged on the inner peripheral surface of the water storage cage,  The first water circulation path has a first opening,  the first filter has a first flushing unit,  the second water circulation path has a second opening,  the second flushing unit,  the second filter has a third flushing unit disposed between the second opening and the second flushing unit,  the second flushing unit disposed at a position lower than the first flushing unit. Even when the washing water level is relatively low,  the washing machine can allow water to pass through the filter with a suitably high hydraulic pressure,  thus not reducing the efficiency of collecting any foreign matters (such as fabric fibers).
sentence_B: 本发明涉及洗衣机， 其中所述第一水循环路径和第二水循环路径在所述储水笼的内周面上设置， 第一水循环路径具有第一开口，第一过滤器具有第一冲洗单元，第二水循环路径具有第二开口，第二冲洗单元，第二过滤器具有设置在第二开口与第二冲洗单元之间的第三冲洗单元，第二冲洗单元设置在低于第一冲洗单元的位置。 这种洗衣机即使在洗涤水位相对较低的情况下，也能使水以适当的高液压通过过滤器，从而不会降低收集任何异物(如织物纤维)的效率。

sentence_A: The invention relates to an aqueous fabric softening composition suitable for use in washing and/or washing cycles of a washing machine,  the composition comprising :  (a) a cationic quaternary ether cellulose polymer in an amount between 0.05% and 2% by mass of the composition;  (b) a soap of fatty acids,  wherein the mass ratio of soap to polymer is at least 2 :  1;  And (c) an amphoteric surfactant in an amount of 0.1% to 5% by mass of the composition. In addition,  the invention also relates to a method of curing a fabric by adding the composition to a washing and/or washing cycle of a washing machine.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种适于在洗衣机洗涤和/或冲洗循环中使用的含水织物柔软组合物，该组合物含有 : (a)阳离子季醚纤维素聚合物，其用量在该组合物的质量0.05%~2%之间； (b)脂肪酸的皂，其中皂与聚合物的质量比最小为2 : 1； 以及(c)两性表面活性剂，其用量为本组合物质量的0.1%~5%。 此外，本发明还涉及通过将该组合物添加到洗衣机洗涤和/或洗衣循环中来养护织物的方法。

sentence_A: A control mechanism (50) comprise a control panel (8),  a control substrate (9),  a power supply substrate (11),  and a protective case (13) having at least two recesses (13a,  13b) and protect that power supply substrate (11) and the control substrate (9) provided in a casing (3) on a casing. The protective shell (13) protects the source base (11) in the recess (13b) and the control base (9) in the residual recess (13a),  and the heat-resistant material (21) is molded in the protective shell (13) between the source base (11) and the control base (9). Therefore,  the control mechanism (50) is compact in structure,  can prevent faults and fault display,  has high reliability,  and can generate a washer having the control mechanism.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种控制机构(50)，包括设置在机壳上外壳(3)中的控制面板(8)，控制基板(9)，电源基板(11)，以及具有至少两个凹部(13a，13b)并保护电源基板(11)和控制基板(9)的保护壳(13)。 保护壳(13)在凹部(13b)保护源基(11)，在残凹部(13a)保护控制基(9)，耐热材料(21)模制在源基(11)和控制基(9)之间的保护壳(13)内。 因此，该控制机构(50)结构紧凑，能够防止故障和故障显示，并且具有高可靠性，并且能够产生具有该控制机构的垫圈。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a gastrointestinal endoscope flushing injection machine which is a device capable of generating pressure and injecting flushing water under a gastrointestinal endoscope. The gastrointestinal endoscope flushing injection machine mainly comprises a pressure generating and water injecting unit,  a control unit and a switch. Open-close. The device adjusts pressure and flow to prevent backflow of fluid from the gastrointestinal tract. The position of the device is suitable for use.
sentence_B: 本发明所述的胃肠内镜冲洗注射机是一种能够产生压力在胃肠内镜下注入冲洗水的装置，主要由产生压力和注水单元、控制单元和开关三部分组成。打开-关闭。该装置可调节压力和流量，以防止液体从胃肠道回流。该装置的位置适合使用。

sentence_A: A control structure (70) comprise a control panel (8) arranged in a casing (3) on a casing,  a control substrate (9) for control,  a power supply substrate (11),  and a protective case (13) having at least two recesses (13a,  13b) and protecting that power supply substrate (11) and the control substrate (9). A protective case (13) protects the power supply substrate (11) at one recess (13b),  and the control substrate (9) is protected at the remaining recesses (13a). A flame retardant material (41) is provided between the bottom (13e) of one recess (13b) of the protective case (13) and the power supply substrate (11). Therefore,  the control mechanism (70) has a compact structure,  can prevent faults and fault display,  and can generate high reliability.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种控制结构(70)，包括设置在机壳上外壳(3)中的控制面板(8)，用于控制的控制基板(9)，电源基板(11)，以及具有至少两个凹部(13a，13b)并保护电源基板(11)和控制基板(9)的保护壳(13)。 保护壳(13)在一个凹部(13b)保护电源基板(11)，在剩余凹部(13a)保护控制基板(9)，保护壳(13)的一个凹部(13b)的底部(13e)和电源基板(11)之间设置阻燃材料(41)。 因此，控制机构(70)结构紧凑，可以防止故障和故障显示，并且可以产生高可靠性。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a chopstick wood manufacturing machine,  which comprises a polishing part and a connecting part,  wherein the polishing part is used for polishing and smoothing wood to obtain a required shape,  and the connecting part is connected between the polishing part and a waste material collecting part. As a passage through which debris or dust generated by polishing of the polishing portion passes to the pickup portion,  the pickup portion adjacent to the connecting portion includes a vacuum cleaner connected to the connecting portion for picking up the debris. Alternatively,  dust generated by the polishing portion reaches a collecting portion through the connecting portion,  the collecting portion being connected to a collecting container on the vacuum cleaner for receiving and collecting the dust. Alternatively,  the dust of the vacuum cleaner reaches the debris collecting portion and the base,  which is made into a groove for mounting the polishing portion,  the connecting portion and the debris collecting portion,  which serves as a base for supporting the polishing portion,  the connecting portion and the debris collecting portion. The polishing part comprises at least one polishing machine,  the grinding wheel of each polishing machine is provided with a surface of abrasive paper with different particle sizes so as to facilitate different polishing,  and the polishing part further comprises a varnish part. Wood varnish for chopsticks
sentence_B: 一种筷子木制造机，包括用于将木材打磨光滑并得到所需形状的抛光部、连接部，该连接部连接在所述抛光部和废料收集部之间。作为由抛光部分的抛光产生的碎片或灰尘通过到拾取部分的通道，与所述连接部分相邻的拾取部分包括与所述连接部分连接的真空吸尘器，用于拾取碎片。或者，由所述抛光部分产生的灰尘通过所述连接部分到达收集部分，所述收集部分连接到所述真空吸尘器上的收集容器用于容纳和收集所述灰尘。或者真空吸尘器的灰尘到达碎片收集部和底座，其被制成用于安装抛光部、连接部和碎片收集部的凹槽，其用作支撑抛光部、连接部和碎片收集部的底座。其中，所述抛光部包括至少1个抛光机，每个抛光机的砂轮具有具有不同粒度的砂纸的表面，以便于不同的抛光，并且还包括清漆部分。用于筷子木清漆

sentence_A: The dishwasher sponge is made of synthetic fiber,  is sprayed with water and waterproof acrylic adhesive,  and is impregnated with polishing abrasive powder for cleaning kitchens. Two types of products can easily clean stains on dishes,  bowls,  pots,  pans,  gas stoves,  refrigerators and microwave ovens,  are not scratched after being used,  and have longer service life;  and the stains on the dishes,  the bowls,  the pots,  the pans,  the gas stoves,  the refrigerators and the microwave ovens can be cleaned easily. The utility model has the advantages of time saving,  labor saving,  cost saving and convenient use.
sentence_B: 洗碗机海绵是由合成纤维制成的，喷水，防水丙烯酸粘合剂，并浸渍抛光砂粉，用于厨房清洁。一种产品中的两种类型，可轻松清洁盘子、碗、锅、平底锅、燃气灶、冰箱和微波炉上的污渍，使用后不划伤，使用寿命更长。使用户既节省时间、人力、成本，又方便使用。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a household electric dish-washing machine,  which is composed of frame bodies of two side walls,  wherein,  the front wall is sealed by metal or plastic,  and both sides of the front wall are perforated,  which is convenient for movement. The rear part is sealed by metal or plastic and is detachable. The lower part of the frame is provided with four tripods. The inner part of the utility model is composed of a hexagonal machine case,  and the utility model is provided with six covers of which the middle parts are folded. The inner part of the utility model is provided with a square central shaft which is provided with a tray which can be used for cleaning bowls and cups. The three angles are respectively composed of perforated metal or plastic pipes with 15 DEG,  20 DEG and 25 DEG. The bottom of the tray is provided with metal or plastic perforations to contain detachable food residues. The top of the utility model is provided with triangular metal or plastic which comprises a rotary switch and a water spraying switch. The switch,  the timing switch and the water pipe hole are closed. The bottom consists of an upper shaft rotating shaft,  a circulator,  a motor and a hose,  and the hose distributes water into the water pipe. Through the operation of the pump,  the water outlet of the pump is provided with a hole which is used for conveying water to the stirrer. The water inlet of the pump is composed of a water inlet and a water outlet. When the machine stops working,  the suction force of the pump does not exist,  and when the machine completes each step,  the discharged water is easy to open,  as previously described.
sentence_B: 家用电动洗碗机由两个侧壁的框架体组成，前壁由金属或塑料封闭，两侧打孔，便于移动。后部部分由金属或塑料封闭，可拆卸。框架的下部是四个三脚架。内部由一个六角形的机箱组成，有一个六个中间折叠的盖子。内部有一个正方形的中心轴，带有一个托盘，可以用来清洗碗和杯。三个角分别由15、20、25度的穿孔金属或塑料管组成。托盘底部有金属或塑料穿孔，以容纳可拆卸的食物残渣。顶部有三角形的金属或塑料，包括旋转和喷水开关。关闭开关、定时开关和水管孔。底部由上轴旋转轴、循环器、电机和软管组成，软管将水分配到水管中。通过泵的工作，泵的出水口有一个孔，用于将水输送到搅拌机。泵的进水口由进水口和出水口两部分组成。当机器停止工作时，泵的吸力不存在，当机器完成每一步时，出水很容易打开，如前所述。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a permanent magnet motor composed of a stator generated by winding a stator winding on the stator,  wherein the stator and rotor are composed of alternating magnetic poles arranged in different polarities. Each permanent magnet is arranged such that the length dimension corresponds to the circumferential dimension of the stator length and the width dimension corresponds to the radial dimension of the stator length. Each permanent magnet has a thickness set such that both ends correspond to the thickness protruding from both ends and correspond to the thickness of the stator length. Each permanent magnet comprises a magnetic powder,  The magnetic powder is sintered and oriented such that the magnetic flux runs circumferentially at the edge relative to the stator,  radially at the edge relative to the stator,  thickly at the edge relative to the stator,  radially at the edge relative to the stator,  and thickly at the edge relative to the stator.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种由定子绕组绕在定子上而产生的定子组成的永磁电机，定子和转子由排列成不同极性交替的磁极组成。 每个永磁体的设置使得长度尺寸与定子长度的圆周尺寸相对应，并且使得宽度尺寸与定子长度的径向尺寸相对应。 每个永久磁铁具有一个厚度，该厚度被设置为使两端与从两端突出的厚度相对应地与定子长度的厚度相对应。 每个永磁体包括一个磁粉体，该磁粉体被烧结和定向，使得磁通在相对于定子的边缘处沿周向运行，在相对于定子的边缘处沿径向运行，在相对于定子的边缘处沿厚度运行，在相对于定子的边缘处沿径向运行，在相对于定子的边缘处沿厚度运行。

sentence_A: The invention provides a face washing device with a polybutylene terephthalate (PBT) cosmetic brush,  wherein the bristles are divided into two sides,  so that the PBT bristles are respectively installed on the inner side and the outer side,  wherein the bristles are round and have sharp inclined surfaces,  and the inner bristles are installed and rotated,  so that the face washing is soft and stable. The washer comprises a box body (100) including a rotating device that rotates when receiving a power supply from the outside;  Batteries;  And rotate the wash brush with the box body. The brush comprises :  a first bristle (610) made of PBT resin and mounted on an output board of an electric motor;  And a second fur (620) mounted on the front outer side surface of the box body,  of the same height,  made of PBT resin,  for surrounding the periphery of the first fur (610) to prevent splashing of external factors during rotation of the first fur (610);  And wherein the first and second plume clusters (611 and 621) have pointed ramps (611A,  621A and LT).
sentence_B: 本发明提出一种具有聚对苯二甲酸丁二酯(PBT)化妆刷的洗脸器，其刷毛基分为两面，使得PBT刷毛分别安装在内侧和外侧，其中刷毛呈圆形且有尖斜面，内侧刷毛安装旋转，使洗脸柔软稳定。 该洗脸器包括 : 箱体(100)，该箱体包括在接收来自外部的电源时旋转的旋转装置；电池； 并将洗脸刷与箱体配合旋转。 该刷包括 : 第一刷毛(610)，由PBT树脂制成，安装在电动马达的输出板上； 以及第二毛皮(620)，安装在盒体的前外侧表面上，高度相同，由PBT树脂制成，用于包围第一毛皮(610)的周边，以防止在第一毛皮(610)的旋转过程中外部因素飞溅； 并且其中第一和第二羽簇(611和621)具有尖头斜面(611A，621A和LT)。

sentence_A: The invention provides an aqueous fabric softening composition,  which is suitable for washing and/or washing process of automatic washing machines and comprises :  (a) a composite anionic surfactant,  the dosage of which is between 0.5 and 4% by weight of the composition;  (b) a soap of fatty acids,  wherein the weight ratio of the synthesized anionic surfactant to the soap of fatty acids is less than 1;  (C) A polymer of cationic quaternary cellulose ether in an amount of 0.05 to 2% by weight of the composition.
sentence_B: 本发明提供一种含水织物柔软组合物，适用于自动洗衣机的洗涤和/或洗衣过程中，其含有 : (a)复合阴离子表面活性剂，其用量在本组合物重量的0.5~4%之间； (b)脂肪酸的皂，其中所合成的阴离子表面活性剂与脂肪酸的皂的重量比小于1； (C)阳离子季纤维素醚的聚合物，其用量为本组合物的0.05~2%重量。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a fabric care composition for use in the washing stage of a washing machine to reduce crease when the fabric is worn. The composition comprises :  a) a dispersion containing nanoparticles with an average particle size in the range of 5 to 500nm,  b) a lubricating phase selected from cationic fabric softener,  silicone oil,  polyester sucrose oil and mixtures thereof,  and c) water in a weight ratio of a) :  b) in the range of 3 :  1 to 1 :  3.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种用于洗衣机洗涤阶段的织物护理组合物，以减少织物穿着时的折皱，该组合物含有 : a)含有平均粒径在5~500nm范围内的纳米粒子的分散体，b)润滑相选自阳离子织物柔软剂，硅油，聚酯蔗糖油及其混合物，c)水，重量比a) : b)在3 : 1~1 : 3范围内。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a vertical washing machine having a double vertical cage (1),  which has a water-tight auxiliary washing rack (6),  which can be easily detached and inserted into a main washing rack (5) for washing light-colored or thin-colored washing objects individually. The sub-laundry cage (6) is provided with fasteners (8),  the base (7) of the sub-laundry cage is fastened on the laundry dish (9),  water flows into the main laundry cage (5) through the pipe (10) and the control valve (11) through the hole (12),  and another water pipe transports water to the sub-laundry cage (6) through the hole (13) of the machine cover (14);  The auxiliary laundry cage (6) has a water outlet pipe (18) installed in the pipe of the drive system (22) for discharging water,  which is discharged into the pipe (20) together with the water outlet pipe (19) of the main laundry cage (5). When it is necessary to wash articles of the same size and volume as bed sheets,  the curtain will remove the auxiliary laundry cage and use it like an ordinary washing machine.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种具有双倍立式保持架(1)的立式洗衣机，其具有水密的辅助洗涤架(6)，可容易地拆卸并插入主洗涤架(5)中，用于单独洗涤浅色或薄色的洗涤物。 副洗衣笼(6)具有紧固件(8)，将副洗衣笼的底座(7)紧固在洗衣盘(9)上，水通过管道(10)和控制阀(11)通过孔(12)流入主洗衣笼(5)，另一水管将水通过机盖(14)的孔(13)输送到副洗衣笼(6)； 辅助洗衣笼(6)具有安装在驱动系统(22)的管道中用于排出水的出水管(18)，它与主洗衣笼(5)的出水管(19)一起排入管道(20)。当需要洗涤像床单一样大小和体积大的物品时，窗帘将辅助洗衣笼拆下，与普通洗衣机一样使用。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a vacuum cleaner and a carpet washer. The utility model is provided with a lower half part,  a water suction pipe and a vacuum cleaner,  wherein,  the side surface of the lower half part is positioned above a viewfinder. Wherein at the top of the lower body is a support cover which is placed on the upper edge of the lower body,  wherein the top of the support cover is an upper body. On the side of the upper half portion,  a water storage container is mounted to contain water and detergent for cleaning the carpet. On the top of the upper half,  there is a control unit to be placed on the upper edge of the upper half. An air suction device and a water pump with a water inlet pipe are arranged at the edge of the control unit,  and water and detergent are sucked into the water storage container for cleaning the carpet and are sucked into the water pipe.
sentence_B: 吸尘器和地毯洗涤器，有一个下半部分，下半部分的侧面位于取景器的上方，有一个吸水管和一个吸尘器。其中，在下半身的顶部是一个支撑盖，该支撑盖被放置在下半身的上边缘上，其中该支撑盖的顶部是一个上半身。在上半部分的侧面，安装了一个储水容器，以容纳用于清洗地毯的水和洗涤剂。在上半部分的顶部，有一个控制单元，将放置在上半部分的上边缘。在控制单元的边缘，安装了一个空气抽吸装置和一个带有进水管的水泵，将水和洗涤剂抽吸到储水容器中，用于清洗地毯，并将其抽吸到水管中。

sentence_A: In the air purification process of the garbage sorting system,  decomposed solid waste is utilized,  and malodorous microorganisms are killed through three sets of deodorants. The utility model is arranged in a garbage classification system. Simultaneously,  odor is sucked through two sets of air inhalers arranged in the garbage classification system. This process. The problem of garbage malodor in the garbage classification system is solved from two aspects of the root and the tail end.
sentence_B: 垃圾分选系统中的空气净化过程是利用经过分解的固体废物，通过三套除臭剂杀灭引起恶臭的微生物。安装在垃圾分类系统中。同时，通过安装在垃圾分类系统中的两套空气吸入器来吸入臭气。这个过程。从根源和末端两个方面解决垃圾分类系统中的垃圾恶臭问题。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a telescopic fixing device of a movable image electronic product. The utility model is composed of a fixing clamp,  a supporting rod and a fixing base. One end of the supporting rod is hingedly fixed on the fixing clamp,  and the other end of the supporting rod is connected with the fixing base which is connected with the movable image electronic product. And the support bar can be retracted. The invention is reliable,  easy to use,  wide application range. The direction of the angle image can be adjusted. The utility model can be used for common vehicles,  such as various vehicles,  etc.,  and can fix the existing movable image electronic products. It has great market potential.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种可移动影像电子产品的可伸缩固定装置。它由固定夹具、支撑杆和固定底座组成。支撑杆在一端铰接地固定在固定夹具上，在另一端连接在固定基座上，所述固定基座与可移动图像电子产品连接。并且这种支撑杆可以缩进。本发明可靠，使用方便，适用范围广。可以调节角度图像的方向。和可移动图像产品的间距，并可用于各种车辆等普通车辆，能够固定现有的可移动图像电子产品。它有很大的市场潜力。

sentence_A: A fabric softener filling system in a dryer fills fabric softeners commonly used in washing machines into products in the washing machine. It was added to the dryer and the fabric softener was delivered to the fabric using equipment to soften the fabric as if the fabric softener was added to the last wash water. The system can be divided into three systems :  1. A fabric softener is added to the oven using an air atomizing nozzle. 2. Fabric softeners were added to the oven using high pressure nozzles. 3. A fabric softener filling system in an oven uses a low pressure nozzle to pass droplets through a bag to bring the bag into contact with fabric in the oven. The fabric softener filling system in the oven is environmentally friendly. The water outlet of the fabric softener in the last washing water is reduced,  the use efficiency of the fabric softener is improved,  and no loss is generated.
sentence_B: 烘干机中的织物柔软剂灌装系统是将通常用于洗衣机中的织物柔软剂灌装到洗衣机中的产品中。将其添加到烘干机中，使用设备将织物柔软剂输送到织物上，使织物柔软，就像将织物柔软剂添加到最后一次洗涤水中一样。可分为3个系统：1。使用空气雾化喷嘴在烘箱中添加织物柔软剂。2。使用高压喷嘴在烘箱中添加织物柔软剂。3。烘箱中的织物柔软剂灌装系统，使用低压喷嘴将雾滴通过袋内，使袋与烘箱中的织物接触。烘箱中的织物柔软剂灌装系统是环保的。减少了织物柔软剂在洗涤最后一次水中的出水，提高了织物柔软剂的使用效率，而不产生任何损失。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a panel (4,  51) mounted on an outer surface portion of an electrical equipment main body (1) and mounted on a main board portion (5,  52),  having display portions (25 to 28) and operation portions (9 to 24) and a light source (37) mounted on a lower surface portion of the main board portion (5,  52) and configured for display by irradiating the display portions (25 to 28) and/or the operation portions (9 to 24). The main board portion (5,  52) is engaged with a decorative plate (41,  53) placed on its surface,  and a support unit (42,  54) made of a non-light transparent material is configured to hold the decorative plate (41,  53),  and the support unit (42,  54) is mounted to the mounting portion (42a),  and the support unit is configured to mount the decorative plate (41,  53) to the main body (1) of the electrical equipment. The decorative plate (41,  53) includes a transparent unit (45,  46),  the transparent unit (45,  46) is mounted to a light blocking layer (47,  57) at least at a lower surface portion thereof,  and the light blocking layer (47,  57) is mounted to a light transmitting part (47a) for display purposes,  wherein the light blocking layer (47,  57) is removed in a colorless state.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及安装在电气设备主体(1)的外表面部分上并安装在主板部分(5，52)上的面板(4，51)，具有显示部分(25至28)和操作部分(9至24)和光源(37)，光源(37)安装在主板部分(5，52)的下表面部分上并通过照射显示部分(25至28)和/或操作部分(9至24)而构成用于显示。 主板部分(5，52)与放置在其表面的装饰板(41，53)接合，由非透光材料制成的支撑单元(42，54)被构成为保持装饰板(41，53)，支撑单元(42，54)被安装到安装部(42a)，该支撑单元被构成为将装饰板(41，53)安装到电气设备的主体(1)上。 装饰板(41，53)包括透明单元(45，46)，透明单元(45，46)至少在其下表面部分安装到挡光层(47，57)，挡光层(47，57)安装到用于显示目的的透光部(47a)，其中挡光层(47，57)在无色状态下被去除。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a quick release joint with a high-voltage boosting safety switch,  which is composed of a main body,  a sliding ring and a rear base. The rear base part is provided with an air through hole at the central position,  the air through hole is divided into two spaces together with the blocking part,  the blocking part is respectively provided with a plurality of through holes at both ends,  and the through holes work simultaneously. With the guide rail is a third circle of the slip ring,  which is connected between the two gaps. The male connector of the high-pressure pressurizing airtight device is locked by sliding the slip ring to open and close the air passage.
sentence_B: 带有高压增压安全开关的快速释放接头由主体、滑动环和后底座组成。后基部在中心位置上具有空气通孔，与阻塞部一起将空气通孔分成两个空间，阻塞部在其两端各有多个通孔，通孔同时工作。带导轨的是滑环的第三个圆圈，它连接在两个间隙之间。通过滑动滑环，打开和关闭空气通道，锁定高压增压气密装置的公接头。

sentence_A: The automatic automobile radiator cleaner according to the present invention is characterized by comprising a water pump for circularly pumping water from the radiator cleaner through an engine cooling system. A conduit from the coolant/cleaning fluid tank is connected to the conduit of the coolant/cleaning fluid tank and pumps liquid into the conduit and out of the pump. The coolant/cleaning fluid tank also provides a conduit connected to the exterior of the vehicle body. The utility model is used for filling and measuring the liquid level in the cooling liquid/cleaning liquid tank. A water inlet pipe portion of the pump for connecting a pipeline of a water pipe flowing out of the automobile coolant system and an area between the water inlet pipes of the pump. A pipeline connected with the automobile cooling system is provided with an anti-backflow valve,  water is prevented from entering the radiator cleaning system through the pipeline,  and the water flows into a pump with a closing valve so as to control external water to enter the system. Moreover. In introducing water from a vehicle cooling system into a conduit of a water pump,  during the formation of a reversing valve,  there is a separate connecting conduit with a shut-off/open valve for draining waste water from the system. To control the operation of the water pump,  various valves are used to control different components. Operation is controlled by control buttons on the control panel.
sentence_B: 根据本发明的自动汽车散热器清洗器的特征是包括用于从散热器清洗器通过发动机冷却系统循环抽水的水泵。从冷却液/清洗液罐的管道连接到冷却液/清洗液罐的管道，并将液体泵送入管道，从泵中流出。冷却液/清洗液罐还提供了一个管道，该管道连接到车身外部。用于在冷却液/清洗液罐内灌装和测量液位。泵的进水管部分，用于连接从汽车冷却液系统流出的水管的管道，以及泵的进水管之间的区域。与汽车冷却系统连接的管道具有防回流阀，防止水通过管道进入散热器清洗系统，并将水流入带有关闭阀的泵中，以控制外部水进入系统。而且。在将车辆冷却系统的水引入水泵的管道上，在形成换向阀的过程中，有一个单独的连接管道，带有关闭/开启阀，用于从系统中排出废水。为了控制水泵的工作，各种阀门用于控制不同的部件。通过控制面板上的控制按钮控制操作。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a power supply mechanism (80),  comprising a power supply substrate (11),  a protective case (13) protecting the power supply substrate (11),  and a flame retardant material (41) disposed between a bottom (13e) of the protective case (13) and the power supply substrate (11),  wherein the power supply substrate (11) has a through hole (42) in a part thereof to determine the presence of the flame retardant material (41). Thus,  the source structure (80) may be compact. In addition,  when manufacturing the power supply structure (80),  it is possible to check or determine whether the flame retardant material (41) exists through the through hole (42) provided in the power supply substrate (11). Thus,  it is possible to prevent the flame retardant material (41) from being not installed. In addition,  the power supply substrate (11) is protected by the flame retardant material (41),  so that the safety of the product can be maintained even in the case of a failure of the high voltage circuit.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种电源机构(80)，包括电源基板(11)，保护电源基板(11)的保护壳(13)和设置在保护壳(13)的底部(13e)与电源基板(11)之间的阻燃材料(41)，其中电源基板(11)在其部分具有通孔(42)，以确定阻燃材料(41)的存在。 因此，源结构(80)可以是紧凑的。 另外，在制造电源结构(80)时，可以通过设置在电源基板(11)中的通孔(42)来检查或确定是否存在阻燃材料(41)。 由此可以防止不安装阻燃材料(41)。 另外，电源基板(11)由阻燃材料(41)保护，因此即使在高压电路发生故障的情况下也能保持产品的安全性。

sentence_B: 新的解释更新9.25599工业吸尘器安装面积平方滤波器41在生产过程中，如成型，辊，非金属冲压，焊接和金属加工。第一部分是由一个螺旋式结构产生的通风流量。第二部分是真空吸尘器的结构调整。过滤装置，空气过滤器和过滤器的清洁，将被放置在一个过滤器，使灰尘再次。3A结构是由矩形的金属制成的，有四层，里面有一个空间，填充九系列过滤器。从工业吸尘器的发明，安装面积平方滤波器41□这是为了提高生产过程中的除尘效率。它可以减少电能消耗，减少灰尘过滤器的安装面积，易于维护。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a length adjusting mechanism of a connecting pipe assembly of a vacuum cleaner,  which comprises a guide member (4) fixedly installed at one end of an outer pipe (1),  and a sliding hole (41) is generated through the guide member (4);  The locking detail (5) can move up and down along the sliding hole (41),  and the lower end of the locking detail (5) is inserted into the locking groove (21) of the inner pipe (2) to fix the inner pipe (2) and the outer pipe (1);  The upper end of the locking member (5) is blocked by a slide (6),  which slide (6) has a groove (61) at the bottom and an inclined side (62) at the top;  The button (8) has an inclined burr (81) so that when the button (8) is pressed,  the inclined burr (81) slides on the inclined side (62) of the slide (6) to push the slide (6) to a position where the locking member (61) is aligned with the locking member (5),  so that the locking member (5) exits the locking slot (21) and enters the locking member (61),  moving the inner tube (2) along the outer tube (1).
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种真空吸尘器的连接管组件长度调节机构，包括固定安装在外管(1)一端的导向件(4)，通过导向件(4)产生滑动孔(41)； 锁定细节(5)可沿滑动孔(41)上下移动，锁定细节(5)的下端插入内管(2)的锁定槽(21)，使内管(2)与外管(1)固定； 滑动件(6)挡住锁定件(5)的上端，这个滑动件(6)在底部有凹槽(61)，在顶部有倾斜的侧面(62)； 按钮(8)具有倾斜毛刺(81)，使得当按下按钮(8)时，倾斜毛刺(81)在滑动件(6)的倾斜侧(62)上滑动，以推动滑动件(6)到锁定件(61)与锁定件(5)对齐的位置，使得锁定件(5)出锁槽(21)并进入锁定件(61)，使内管(2)沿外管(1)移动。

sentence_A: The invention relates to an intermediate bulk raw material storage container (1) for storing or transporting granular catalytic raw materials,  comprising a container (2),  the inner wall of which is a granular catalytic raw material generating container volume. The container (20) includes a cylindrical member (22),  an upper plate (28) sealing the upper end of the cylindrical member (22),  and a bottom portion (24) connected from the lower end of the cylindrical member (22) and tapered inwardly. A hole (30) is provided in a side plate (28) of a container (20) for receiving catalytic raw materials,  and a seal (32) for sealing the hole (30) is provided. When the aperture (30) has been closed by the seal (32),  an air seal is configured. An air duct (38) is connected to the container (20) to provide inert gas to the sealed container (20) or to withdraw gas from the container (20),  thereby applying a vacuum in the container (20) to reduce the risk of fire. The gas pipeline is sealed by a valve (40) for transportation or storage.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种用于储存或运输粒状催化原料的中间散装原料储存容器(1)，包括容器(2)，其内壁为粒状催化原料产生容器容积。 容器(20)包括圆筒形部件(22)，密封圆筒形部件(22)上端的上板(28)和从圆筒形部件(22)下端连接并向内锥形底部部分(24)。 在用于接收催化原料的容器(20)的侧板(28)中设置有孔(30)，并设置有密封孔(30)的密封件(32)。 当孔(30)已经被密封件(32)关闭时，配置空气密封件。 空气管道(38)连接到容器(20)，以向已密封的容器(20)提供惰性气体或从容器(20)中抽出气体，从而在容器(20)中施加真空以降低火灾风险。 气体管道由阀门(40)密封，用于运输或储存。

sentence_A: The present invention relates to a fume exhausting device for sucking oil fume produced by electric crane in various operating rooms or sanatoriums. sentence_B: 本发明所述的排烟装置是用于在各种手术室或疗养院中，用电吊机抽吸电吊产生的油烟的排烟装置，其特征在于：该排烟装置包括一个排烟容器；在将气味和烟雾输送到烟道后，将气味和烟雾输送到吸入器中，以保持气味和烟雾。该装置能够很好地吸收气味和烟雾。这有助于减少燃烧的气味和电劫持的烟雾造成的污染。

sentence_A: The extrusion molding unit comprises a base,  a receiving platform,  at least one projector,  an extrusion template and a heater,  wherein the base comprises a material feeding area and a molding area,  and the receiving platform moves from the material feeding area to the molding area. sentence_B: 所述挤压成形单元包括：底座、接收平台、至少一个投影仪、挤压模板和加热器，所述底座包括材料进料区和成形区，所述接收平台从所述材料进料区移动到所述成形区中。以及当其处于材料进料区时，在接收平台上堆叠多个连接片，至少一个投影仪固定在材料进料区上方，以便将多个对准图像投射到接收平台上，在该接收平台上放置多个对准图像。每个连接片通过与每个对准图像对齐而堆叠在接收平台上，压缩模板被布置在成形区上方，并且当接收平台移动到成形区上时，所述压缩模板被放置在接收平台上。压缩模板移动以压缩受热架上的每个连接件，受热架安装在底座上以加热受热架上的每个连接件。

sentence_A: The artificial camouflage net is a quadrangular camouflage net,  the length of each side is 4 meters,  the diagonal length of the short side is 4 meters,  the artificial camouflage net is composed of two layers of materials,  the bottom layer is a net,  and the net frame is formed by weaving synthetic fiber materials. Saving and unifying standards

sentence_A: The invention relates to a roll-up paper bag adhesive for packaging agricultural products on trees. The adhesive can not be stuck on the hand of a user,  and is firm in sticking,  high in speed and durable in use. The adhesive can be disassembled and reclosed. It is a water-insoluble adhesive. In addition,  under the sunlight,  any oil or liquid can not seep out. The utility model has the advantages of low cost,  no toxicity to the environment,  easy degradation and no garbage in the future. Materials used by the utility model are easy to obtain,  and the utility model also exists in China. Before the utility model is used,  an adhesive tape is arranged to prevent the adhesive tape from sticking on the bag opening. The adhesive tape can be easily pulled out. When the bag mouth is sealed,  ants,  insects and small foreign matters can not enter the bag.
sentence_B: 本发明是一种用于包装树上农产品的卷口纸袋胶粘剂的发明。这种胶粘剂不会粘在使用者的手上，粘得牢固，速度快，经久耐用。胶粘剂可以拆开再重新封闭。它是一种不溶于水的胶粘剂。而且在阳光下，不会渗出任何油或液体，价格便宜，对环境无毒，来自大自然，易于降解，将来不会成为垃圾，使用的材料很容易获得，国内也有。在使用前，有一条胶粘剂带，防止粘在袋口上。这条胶粘剂带很容易拔出。当封住袋口时，蚂蚁、昆虫和小异物不会进入袋内。

sentence_A: The DNA extraction kit according to the invention comprises a packaging box,  wherein the inner part of the packaging box comprises A (1 bottle of salt),  B (1 bottle of dishwashing liquid),  C (1 bottle of 70% isopropyl alcohol dishwashing liquid),  a teaspoon,  a plurality of white fabrics,  a plastic bag and a small rod. A transparent plastic cup and a simple DNA extraction file. This simple DNA extraction kit does not require any electrical equipment. It uses dishwashing liquid rather than chemicals to destroy cells. Salt is used to aid in the non-rejection of anions of DNA,  and alcohol is used to wash the wound to precipitate DNA.
sentence_B: 根据本发明的DNA提取试剂盒包括一个包装盒，其内部包括A(1瓶食盐)、B(1瓶洗碗液)、C(1瓶70%异丙醇洗碗液)、茶匙、一些白色织物、塑料袋、小棒。一个透明的塑料杯和一个简单的DNA提取文件。这个简单的DNA提取试剂盒不需要任何电气设备。它使用洗碗液而不是化学物质来破坏细胞。用食盐来帮助DNA的阴离子不排斥，用酒精来清洗伤口使DNA沉淀。

sentence_A: Palm oil is a natural substance and is used for producing dishwasher detergents,  toilet bowl and sanitary ware surface detergents or laundry soaps instead of the chemical substance sodium dodecyl ether sulfate.

sentence_A: The door lock device is arranged in a room for unlocking the active door,  and the width of an unlocking gap is not more than 4,  so that the door lock device can be locked inside and outside the room by an owner of the room. The fingers are wide enough that only hands can pass through and unlock the lock,  so that the room is safe.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a safe (1),  wherein the safe comprises a fuse box body (10),  at least one side of the fuse box body having a door (11) having a door lock system (12) comprising a movable key position (121) for creating a locked state between the door (11) and the fuse box body (10). The door lock system (12) also has a frangible member fixedly disposed inside the door (11),  which drives at least one safety pin (123),  which keeps the movable key position (121) in a locked state when the frangible member breaks. The safe (1) can solve the problem of weak areas in the known safe,  and the safe according to the invention has low price and high reliability.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种保险箱(1)，其中此保险箱包括保险箱体(10)，保险箱体的至少一侧具有门(11)，此门具有门锁系统(12)，此门锁系统(12)包括用于在门(11)和保险箱体(10)之间产生锁紧状态的活动键位(121)。 门锁系统(12)还具有固定设置在门(11)内侧的易碎件，此易碎件驱动至少一个安全销(123)，当易碎件断裂时，安全销(123)保持可移动键位(121)处于锁定状态。 保险箱(1)可以解决已知保险箱中存在薄弱区域的问题，根据本发明的保险箱价格低，可靠性高。

sentence_A: The present invention provides a fragrant stylus pen made up by combining cylinders made of non-metallic material. Said ink device disposed within said cartridge;  The pressure device is arranged on the top of the barrel;  A distal end portion provided at the bottom of the cylinder and a contact head provided on the distal end portion and provided with a slit for an ink device through the portion,  the entire non-metallic cylinder. And said distal end portion being coated with an electroplated layer on said conductive surface to conduct said electricity to a touch screen of said electronic product by passing an electrostatic current from said operator through said touch head;  A cylindrical body having an outer surface provided with at least a receiving groove and at least an incense block disposed in the receiving groove;  The smell of the fragrance block changes with the change of the temperature.
sentence_B: 本发明提供一种由非金属材料制成的圆筒组合而成的有香味的手写笔；所述油墨装置，所述油墨装置设置在所述筒内；所述压力装置设置在所述筒体的顶部；设置在所述圆筒底部的远端部和设置在所述远端部上并通过所述部分设置用于油墨装置的狭缝的接触头，所述整个非金属圆筒。以及所述远端部在所述导电表面上涂有一层电镀层，以便通过从所述操作人员的静电电流通过所述触摸头将所述电传导到所述电子产品的触摸屏上；一种筒体，其外表面至少设置有接收槽，并且至少设置在接收槽中的香块；香块的气味随着温度的变化而变化。

sentence_A: The electronic product display board with the user interaction function can display the shapes of 40 electronic products,  and can be used as a teaching material for electronic technicians. Each person can study anytime and anywhere.
sentence_B: 具有用户交互功能的电子产品展板，可显示40个电子产品的形状，可作为电子技术人员的教学材料。每个人都可以随时随地学习。

sentence_A: The invention provides a common mechanical lock with anti-theft electronic components. Anti-theft electronic components consist of mechanical blocks and electronic blocks. The muscle block comprises a key locking pin,  and the key locking pin comprises a structural shell,  an electromagnet and a motion key locking pin. The key lock is automatically controlled. The latch control electronic block includes a filling source section,  a digital code setting section,  a digital code input section,  and a central processing section for confirming the input digital code according to the input code confirmation result that controls the latch to rise or not to rise. The central processing unit section has two processors,  one of which operates in a standby state. The central processing section also switches the feed power supply from the grid power supply to the standby battery power supply in blocks. The digital code setting part adopts a simple switch combination designed according to 10x10 matrix. By adopting this technical scheme,  the householder does not need to replace the whole lock,  but still can obtain higher safety than the traditional mechanical door lock.
sentence_B: 本发明提供一种具有防盗电子部件的普通机械的锁。 防盗电子部件由机械块和电子块组成。 所述肌肉块包括一键锁销，所述键锁销包括一结构壳体，一电磁铁，一运动键锁销。 钥匙锁是自动控制的。 所述锁存器控制电子块包括加注源部分，数字代码设置部分，数字代码输入部分，以及用于根据控制锁存器升高或不升高的输入代码确认结果来确认输入数字代码的中央处理部分。 中央处理器部分具有两个处理器，两个处理器中的一个在备用状态下工作。 中央处理部分还分块地将馈电电源从电网电源切换到备用电池电源。 数字代码设置部分采用了按10x10矩阵设计的简单开关开关组合。 采用这种技术方案，户主不必更换整把锁，但仍可获得比传统机械门锁更高的安全性。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a one-way ticket IC card recovery system for a railway ticketing system. The recovery system is a recovery system that uses an IC card for one-way travel tickets (11) and uses the IC card again. A recovery system,  for example,  a card vending machine (200) provided at a departure station and equipped with a distribution assembly (202),  a distribution assembly (100) provided at the departure station and equipped with a recovery assembly (301),  and a ticketing line shielding device (300),  the recovery assembly having a ballot box (100). Generally,  a card vending machine (200) and a ticketing barricade device (300) are provided at each station. The ballot boxes for the assigned cluster and the ballot boxes for the restored cluster that have been used are public ballot boxes. The universal ballot box (100) has a screen door (101) that opens the cartridge opening portion (104) during loading and closes the cartridge opening portion during transportation.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种用于铁路售票系统的单程车票IC卡回收系统。 这个恢复系统是一个将IC卡用于单程旅行票(11)的恢复系统，并再次使用这个IC卡。 一种恢复系统，例如设置在发车站并安装分配组件(202)的售卡机(200)，设置在发车站并安装恢复组件(301)的分配组件(100)和售票线路屏蔽装置(300)，恢复组件具有票箱(100)。 通常，在每个车站都设置有售卡机(200)和售票路障设备(300)。 分配群集的票箱和已使用的恢复群集的票箱是公用票箱。 通用票箱(100)具有一个屏蔽门(101)，该屏蔽门在装载时打开卡座口部分(104)，在运输时关闭这个卡座口部分。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a filter (11) for a cleaning device,  which is arranged in a water supply line through which water from an external water source is transported. The filter (11) comprises a filter cartridge (14),  a bayonet (23),  a filter medium (24) and a blocking plate (25). The filter box (14) is in detail in the form of a container having a water inlet (15) at one end and a water outlet (16) at the other end. A card (23) is arranged in the filter cartridge (14) so that the card is located between the feed port (15) and the discharge port (16) in the filter cartridge. An aperture (23) having a cylindrical wall having a perforated aperture (23a) is created. The filter medium (24) consists of a garment fabric wrapped in a cylindrical shape and held by a drum (23). The blocking plate (25) is supported on one end of the bayonet (23) and has a surface opposite to the flow direction of water from the inlet port of the filter box (14). After the water from the air inlet (15) is collected by the blocking plate (25),  the filter (11) causes the water to flow from the outer peripheral side of the filter medium (24) to the middle to remove impurities in the water.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种用于清洗装置的过滤器(11)，其设置在供水管路中，从外部水源的水通过其输送。 过滤器(11)包括过滤盒(14)，卡口(23)，过滤介质(24)和阻塞板(25)。 过滤箱(14)详细地为容器形式，其一端具有进水口(15)，另一端具有出水口(16)。 在过滤盒(14)中设置有卡片(23)，使得卡片位于过滤盒中的进料口(15)和出料口(16)之间。 产生具有圆柱形壁的孔(23)，该圆柱形壁具有穿孔孔(23a)。 过滤介质(24)由包绕成圆筒状并由卷筒(23)保持的服装织物组成。 阻塞板(25)支承在卡口(23)的一端上，并且具有与水从过滤箱(14)的进气道的流动方向相反的表面。 在来自进气口(15)的水被阻塞板(25)收集后，过滤器(11)使水产生从过滤介质(24)的外周侧向中间的流动，以去除水中的杂质。

sentence_A: The cabinet and the air cable connector are composed of three main parts :  1. A cabinet and a connector for covering the internal components to prevent rain and dust;  2. The foamed rubber strip is used for covering the two ends to prevent rainwater and dust. And a guide rail and a guide rail bracket portion for mounting the lightning arrester. The cabinet and the top connector have hoops for suspending the cabinet on the bridge. When the three locking rings are released and the box body is used,  the front cover is opened downwards. The guide rail and the guide rail bracket are arranged on the base. The guide rail bracket is used for installing the cable bracket and is used as a connecting point between a telephone line and a power distribution line. The back is the connecting point of the telephone line,  and the middle is provided with a plastic baffle plate. The interior of the cabinet is divided into two parts. The distributor reaches the customer's home through a rubber ball connected to the cabinet base. When the utility model is used as a connector for connecting telephone lines,  a guide rail and a guide rail bracket do not need to be installed. The utility model is developed from an airborne cable connector,  can be used as a machine case and can also be used as a machine case connector. This reduces the installation cost and labor cost,  the working time is reduced.
sentence_B: 机箱和空气电缆连接器由三个主要部件组成：1。机箱和连接器，用于覆盖内部部件，以防止雨水和灰尘；2。泡沫橡胶条，用于覆盖两端，以防止雨水和灰尘。以及用于安装避雷器的导轨和导轨托架部分。箱体和顶部连接器具有用于将箱体悬挂在桥架上的卡箍。当释放三个锁环时，当箱体使用时，前盖将向下打开。导轨和导轨托架安装在底座上。导轨托架用于安装电缆托架，作为电话线与配电线之间的连接点。后面是电话线的连接点，中间有一块塑料隔板。并将机柜内部分隔成两部分。配线器通过连接在机柜底座上的橡胶球来到达客户的家。当它作为连接电话线的连接器时，不需要安装导轨和导轨支架。从机载电缆连接器发展而来，既可作为机箱使用，也可作为机箱连接器使用。这降低了安装成本和人工成本，减少了工作时间。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a method for improving the stability of Bayer solution,  which comprises the step of contacting Bayer solution with low molecular weight glucan in an amount of one part per million (PPM). In addition,  the invention also relates to a method for controlling the process of precipitating aluminum-containing compounds from Bayer solutions.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种提高拜耳溶液稳定性的方法，该方法包括使拜耳溶液以百万分之一(PPM)的量与低分子量葡聚糖接触的步骤。此外，本发明还涉及控制从拜耳溶液中析出含铝化合物的过程的方法。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a fabric softening composition,  which comprises :  (a) 0.01% to 50% mass fraction of cationic or nonionic softening compounds;  (b) at least 0.001 mas percent of that water-dispersed crosslink cationic polymer is formed by polymerizing 5 to 100 mole percent of monomer with vinyl cations,  From 0% to 95% by mole of acrylamide,  And the copolyvinyl monomer crosslinking agent of 5ppm to 500ppm has two functional groups (C) of 0% to 5% of the mass of free aromatic oil,  (d) at least one cystic fabric or skin care component in the organic polymer,  the effective amount of which is present on the outside of the polymer,  the hydroxyl-oxygen functional group being attached thereto,  thereby creating an outer shell on at least a portion,  the outer shell being capable of permeating fragrance,  and the polymer having the hydroxyl-oxygen functional group not being moved into water for a long time;  And (e) the rest is water and any one or more auxiliary substances.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种织物柔软组合物，其含有 : (a)0.01%~50%质量分数的阳离子或非离子柔软化合物； (b)至少0.001%质量分数的水分散交联阳离子聚合物是由5%~100%摩尔单体加乙烯基阳离子聚合而成， 从0%到95%摩尔丙烯酰胺， 以及5ppm~500ppm的共聚乙烯基单体交联剂具有2个官能团(C)为游离芳烃油质量的0%~5%， (d)在有机聚合物中的至少一个囊状织物或护肤成分，其有效量存在于该聚合物的外侧，所述氢氧官能团连接在其上，从而在至少一部分上创建一个外壳，所述外壳可以使芳香剂渗透，并且所述具有氢氧官能团的聚合物长期不移入水中； 和(e)其余的是水和任意的一种或多种辅助物质。

sentence_A: The purpose of the rice boiling machine is to solve the problem of the soaking process caused by the fact that rice boiling needs to be cleaned for a long time. Because a large amount of rice can not be produced,  the inventor invents a glutinous rice steaming and boiling machine. In order to reduce the workload of cooking glutinous rice,  shorten the soaking time of manufacturers and facilitate the operation,  the invention discloses a cooking glutinous rice cleaning machine. The cooking glutinous rice cleaning machine is characterized by comprising three main parts,  namely a cleaning machine,  an extruder and a warm water system,  so that the problems are solved and the production efficiency is improved.
sentence_B: 煮米机的目的是为了解决由于煮米需要很长时间来清洗而导致的浸泡过程的问题。由于无法生产大量的大米，发明者发明了蒸煮糯米机。为了减轻蒸煮糯米的工作负担，缩短生产厂家的浸泡时间，方便操作，我们发明了蒸煮糯米清洗机，其特点是：该系统由三个主要部分组成，分别是清洗机、挤压机和温水系统，以解决出现的问题，提高生产效率。

sentence_B: เครื่องทำลมแห้งแบบใช้ลมเป่าสำหรับเครื่องล้างรถ โดยในส่วนของเครื่องเป่าลมจะมีรูนำอากาศยาวโดยหันไปทางแต่ละด้านของตัวรถ และแผ่นวัสดุที่ยื่นออกมาขนานกันจะจัดเรียงอยู่ด้านใดด้านหนึ่ง หรือในแต่ละด้าน ด้านข้างของช่องสัญญาณออกอากาศ และยิ่งไปกว่านั้น แถวของร่องจะมีให้ที่ปลายด้านหนึ่งของแผ่นวัสดุแต่ละแผ่นเพื่อสร้างแถบวัสดุจำนวนหนึ่ง อาจมีการจัดเรียงแถวของแผ่นวัสดุเชื่อมต่อระหว่างแผ่นวัสดุด้านข้างสองแผ่นของช่องแนะนำการออกอากาศแต่ละช่อง อากาศที่พุ่งออกจากช่องนำร่องออกอากาศจะดีดแผ่นวัสดุที่หมุนออก และเพื่อการซักอย่างรวดเร็วด้วยการแตะและเป่าให้พื้นผิวรถแห้ง ซึ่งช่วยประหยัดเวลาและความพยายาม และปรับปรุงประสิทธิภาพของการล้างรถ

sentence_A: 本发明涉及一种皮卡端盖，端盖中间只有一个手柄。用户将能够正确地锁定和解锁现有的锁止机构，无论是使用车门中央锁的电气系统还是使用钥匙。因此，可以关闭尾门并将其完全锁定。
sentence_B: เครื่องทดสอบความล้าของคานเท้าแขนแบบหนีบสปริงประกอบด้วยชุดรองรับ ชุดสตาร์ทกำลัง ชุดส่งกำลัง ชุดแคลมป์ และชุดถ่วงน้ำหนัก เป็นเครื่องทดสอบโหลดแบบลูกสูบต่อเนื่อง (โหลดแบบวนรอบ) หรือความล้าของวัสดุเครื่องจักรหรืออุปกรณ์ก่อนใช้งาน การปรับปรุงส่วนประกอบอุปกรณ์สามารถทำได้ก่อนที่จะสร้างเครื่องจักร เครื่องทดสอบความล้ามีอุปกรณ์จับยึดแบบสปริงที่ยึดชิ้นงานทดสอบอย่างแน่นหนาในระหว่างการทดสอบโดยไม่ลื่นไถล อุปกรณ์ส่งกำลังใช้ข้อต่อร่องสากล เพื่อแก้ปัญหาการล็อคตัวเองของคัปปลิ้ง ระยะการเคลื่อนที่จะเพิ่มขึ้น เหมาะสำหรับการทดสอบความล้าของวัสดุและตะกั่วในเชิงพาณิชย์

sentence_A: 煮米机的目的是为了解决由于煮米需要很长时间来清洗而导致的浸泡过程的问题。由于无法生产大量的大米，发明者发明了蒸煮糯米机。为了减轻蒸煮糯米的工作负担，缩短生产厂家的浸泡时间，方便操作，我们发明了蒸煮糯米清洗机，其特点是：该系统由三个主要部分组成，分别是清洗机、挤压机和温水系统，以解决出现的问题，提高生产效率。
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề xuất hệ thống và phương pháp phát hiện màn chắn dấu giám sát vật phẩm điện tử (EAS),  hệ thống này bao gồm hệ thống phụ giám sát vật phẩm điện tử,  hệ thống phụ phát hiện kim loại và hệ thống phụ phân tích hình ảnh được ghép truyền thông với bộ điều khiển hệ thống. Hệ thống phụ EAS có tác dụng phát hiện các dấu EAS trong vùng phát hiện. Hệ thống phụ phát hiện kim loại có tác dụng phát hiện các vật kim loại trong vùng phát hiện. Hệ thống phụ phân tích hình ảnh có tác dụng chụp lại hình ảnh của vật kim loại. Bộ điều khiển hệ thống có tác dụng xác định phân loại thống kê đối với vật kim loại này và tính toán trọng số tin cậy đối với phân loại thống kê này. Nếu vật kim loại này được nhận diện là màn chắn dấu EAS theo phân loại thống kê này và trọng số tin cậy tương ứng,  thì tín hiệu cảnh báo sẽ được phát ra.

sentence_A: 一种带有中控锁系统的车辆的移动门锁系统，该系统包括安装在车辆中的移动门锁，以接收来自个人或其他移动门锁的信号。用户必须有4位代码才能用手机与解锁系统通信。这4位代码是唯一可编程的，2位代码用于锁定和解锁。
sentence_B: 一种开口锁紧装置，包括两部分，其中一部分固定在开口的一侧或固定在开口的框架上，耳朵突出在开口的表面或框架上。第二部分固定在另一开口上，其中所述第二部分的端部具有盒状物，所述盒状物具有用于嵌入所述锁的开口。其中，该挂锁为U形挂锁，其特征是与盒体一致，并且其设置方式是，当打开的门关闭并按压该挂锁的锁杆时，该挂锁的锁杆与第一部分的突出耳对齐。锁杆的端部被插入钩环中，所以当钩环处于锁定状态时，钩环隐藏在箱体内时，窃贼无法切割钩环。

sentence_A: A closed force transmission structure is provide in which that mounting depth of the mount pin to the mounting pin groove can be adjusted to increase safety strength and structural components can be simplified to allow easy assembly and increase strength. The invention also provides a safety door lock using the structure. The closed force transmission mechanism according to the present invention includes a cylindrical body shell,  both sides of which are opened to penetrate the door;  The main body is slidably arranged in the main body housing so that the main body moves in a linear direction by a force acting from the outside,  the main body has at least one inclined surface,  and the movement space of the main body generates a direction perpendicular to the linear movement direction at a part corresponding to the inclined surface;  The handle is connected to the main body and extends outward from both sides of the door. And a fixing mechanism,  one end of which passes through the movement space of the main body and is connected with the main body,  so that one end of the fixing mechanism can move perpendicularly to the movement direction of the main body,  and the other end of the fixing mechanism can be elastically supported at the main body shell,  so that the fixing mechanism can move perpendicularly to the movement direction of the main body and is interlocked with the linear movement of the main body.
sentence_B: 本发明提出了一种电子物品监测(EAS)标志屏检测系统和方法，该系统包括与系统控制器通信的电子物品监测子系统，金属检测子系统和图像分析子系统。 所述EAS子系统具有检测所述检测区域中的EAS标记的效果。 金属检测子系统具有检测检测区域内金属物体的效果。 图像分析子系统具有对金属物体图像进行重拍的效果。 系统控制器具有确定此金属对象的统计分类和计算此统计分类的置信度权重的作用。 如果这个金属物体根据这个统计分类和相应的置信权重被识别为EAS标志屏，那么就会发出报警信号。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a vertical washing machine having a double vertical cage (1),  which has a water-tight auxiliary washing rack (6),  which can be easily detached and inserted into a main washing rack (5) for washing light-colored or thin-colored washing objects individually. The sub-laundry cage (6) is provided with fasteners (8),  the base (7) of the sub-laundry cage is fastened on the laundry dish (9),  water flows into the main laundry cage (5) through the pipe (10) and the control valve (11) through the hole (12),  and another water pipe transports water to the sub-laundry cage (6) through the hole (13) of the machine cover (14);  The auxiliary laundry cage (6) has a water outlet pipe (18) installed in the pipe of the drive system (22) for discharging water,  which is discharged into the pipe (20) together with the water outlet pipe (19) of the main laundry cage (5). When it is necessary to wash articles of the same size and volume as bed sheets,  the curtain will remove the auxiliary laundry cage and use it like an ordinary washing machine.
sentence_B: ฟองน้ำเครื่องล้างจานทําจากเส้นใยสังเคราะห์สเปรย์น้ํากาวอะคริลิกกันน้ําและจุ่มผงทรายขัดใช้สําหรับทําความสะอาดครัว สองประเภทของผลิตภัณฑ์ที่สามารถทำความสะอาดจานชามหม้อกระทะก๊าซเตาตู้เย็นและเตาไมโครเวฟโดยไม่มีรอยขีดข่วนและอายุการใช้งานนาน ช่วยให้ผู้ใช้ประหยัดเวลากำลังคนค่าใช้จ่ายและใช้งานง่าย

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine operation display device and a washing machine mounted with the device,  Wherein the device has a selection press button for determining an operation process of washing and drying operation conditions,  a liquid crystal plate for displaying setting conditions of setting the press button and washing,  drying and extrusion,  the transparent plate having transparent electrodes,  and the transparent plate is superimposed on the liquid crystal plate. The touch panel is also installed to perform an operation by touching a finger to the transparent panel,  and a descriptive display screen (71) describing details of the operation program is inserted into the touch panel. The process setting press button (67) causes the liquid crystal panel to display setting conditions,  and the setting press button is also arranged on the descriptive display screen (71).
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập tới nồi nấu chân không,  trong đó tay cầm nắp có chức năng chân không và chức năng chống tràn được lắp trên nắp dùng cho nồi nấu chân không,  và nắp được khoá với phần chứa nhờ sử dụng bộ phận khoá được lắp ở tay xách phần chứa.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a permanent magnet motor composed of a stator generated by winding a stator winding on the stator,  wherein the stator and rotor are composed of alternating magnetic poles arranged in different polarities. Each permanent magnet is arranged such that the length dimension corresponds to the circumferential dimension of the stator length and the width dimension corresponds to the radial dimension of the stator length. Each permanent magnet has a thickness set such that both ends correspond to the thickness protruding from both ends and correspond to the thickness of the stator length. Each permanent magnet comprises a magnetic powder,  The magnetic powder is sintered and oriented such that the magnetic flux runs circumferentially at the edge relative to the stator,  radially at the edge relative to the stator,  thickly at the edge relative to the stator,  radially at the edge relative to the stator,  and thickly at the edge relative to the stator.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt bao gồm lồng giặt để giặt,  giũ và vắt khô đồ giặt,  nắp mở và đóng ô cửa,  bộ phận phát hiện việc mở và đóng nắp,  bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt để phát hiện sự có mặt hoặc không có mặt của đồ giặt trong lồng giặt,  bộ phận sấy khô lồng giặt,  và thiết bị điều khiển để điều khiển bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt sao cho sự có mặt hoặc không có mặt của đồ giặt trong lồng giặt được phát hiện bởi bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt khi việc mở và đóng nắp được phát hiện bởi bộ phận phát hiện việc mở và đóng nắp sau khi công đoạn giặt đã được kết thúc. Thiết bị điều khiển còn điều khiển bộ phận sấy khô lồng giặt sao cho công đoạn sấy khô lồng giặt được thực hiện bởi bộ phận sấy khô lồng giặt khi bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt cho biết rằng không có đồ giặt trong lồng giặt.

sentence_A: An apparatus for locking a pick-up rear rim to a side rim of a pick-up rear wheel overhead base includes an outer pick-up base having a side rim line and a top locking base having a downwardly curved top as an abutting edge. An upper side edge,  a pick-up end and a bottom locking base for press-fitting into an overhead base,  characterized in that the pick-up base has an upwardly curved portion as a bottom press-fitting edge. The utility model is used for pressing in the lower side edge of the tail door. Between the side edges of the outsole locking base,  there is an insertion rod between the edges having through holes for supporting rotation by external threads of the inner insertion rod inserted from the through holes of the locking base. There is also a bottom of the insertion portion at the gap between the side edges.
sentence_B: ตัวล็อคสำหรับล็อคหน้าจอมีลักษณะที่ประกอบด้วยส่วนฐาน และส่วนด้านข้างของส่วนฐานแต่ละส่วนมีเบาะสำหรับป้องกันขอบของกรอบหน้าต่างจับจ้องอยู่ที่ขอบของกรอบหน้าต่างหรือขอบของ วงกบประตูจากการล้ม พร้อมทั้งมีก้านยื่นออกมาจากด้านนอกของส่วนฐานสำหรับล็อคประตูมุ้งลวดเข้ากับกรอบหน้าต่างหรือวงกบประตู และในพื้นที่ส่วนกลางของส่วนฐานจะมีรูพรุนเพื่อนำน็อตล็อคไปที่ขอบของกรอบหน้าต่างหรือประตู

sentence_A: The locking-releasing mechanism includes an elongated opening into which the support tube is inserted and on which a key with the locking-releasing mechanism is mounted. The utility model is used for transmitting force from the key to cause the lock bolt to slide-the lock is screwed into the lock hole of the inner cannula. And a side surface inserted into the support tube to form a side sliding groove,  wherein a part of the side sliding groove forms a side connecting groove. For moving a portion of the inner surface of the groove to the inner shoulder edge of the groove and laterally connecting a portion of the groove to connect the groove to the bottom open edge. A sliding channel for an inwardly inserted laterally projecting rod is characterized by an elongated inner hollow rod or tube for inwardly inserting a support tube. And an outwardly penetrating spring rod disposed in the outer region of the inner insert rod for supporting the pressure transmitted from the outside,  and a locking hole disposed in a part of the side surface of the inner insert rod. An in-out lock for supporting a key latch.
sentence_B: เครื่องซักผ้าขนาดเล็กแบบพกพา (portable mini-washer) ที่มีกรอบภายนอก (casing),  ถ้วยการซักล้าง และ หน้าต่างที่โปร่งใสบนกรอบภายนอก กรอบภายนอก กำหนดพื้นที่ว่างภายใน และมีหน้าด้านหน้า,  หน้าด้านข้างซ้ายในการเชื่อมต่อทางด้านข้างกับหน้าด้านหน้า,  หน้าด้านข้างขวาในการเชื่อมต่อทางด้านข้างกับหน้าด้านหน้า และ ทางด้านตรงกันข้ามกับหน้าด้านข้างซ้าย และ หน้าด้านบนในการเชื่อมต่อในแนวตั้งกับหน้าด้านหน้า,  หน้าด้านข้างซ้าย และ หน้าด้านข้างขวา ถ้วยการซักล้างรวมถึงในที่นั้นด้วยเครื่องมือทำการคน และ ส่วนที่โปร่งใสที่ซึ่งหันหน้าเข้าหาหน้าต่างที่โปร่งใสของกรอบภายนอก กรอบภายนอก และ ถ้วยการซักล้างถูกผลิตอย่างแยกจากกัน;  และ ถ้วยการซักล้างถูกวาง และ ตรึงในพื้นที่ว่างภายใน

sentence_A: The door and window locking device comprises a locking plate which is blocked from rotating by a lever with a spring ring so as to provide the feeling of locking and keep the locking plate in the base. The lock body is provided with a cylinder for supporting the lever,  so that the lock body is firm. The lock seat is provided with a groove which causes the lever to keep about 180 DEG,  and therefore,  the operation is slippery. A circular lock plate of the lock seat is laterally cut to be hidden in the lock seat. Grooves for inserting the lock cover and the lock cover are also provided.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy rửa bát bao gồm thùng máy (50) có ba ngăn riêng biệt bao gồm ngăn cửa,  ngăn rửa và ngăn tráng;  trục quay (24) được bố trí tại tâm của trụ tròn của máy rửa bát,  một đầu của trục quay (24) được nối với giá đựng bát (2) để dẫn động giá đựng bát này,  đầu còn lại được nối với bộ giảm tốc của động cơ. Ngăn cửa gồm có nắp đậy,  bảng điều khiển (11),  máng hứng nước rơi vãi (4). Ngăn rửa được chia làm hai khoang nhỏ,  khoang chứa nước rửa ở bên phải,  bên trong khoang này có phao nước (141) và một lỗ thoát nước nhỏ để nối với ống nước thải ra ngoài (101);  bên trái là khoang chống tràn,  ngăn giữa hai khoang này là tấm ngăn cách (16);  ba cột phun nước (121);  khay lưới lọc (13),  tấm hứng nước dồn vào khay lưới lọc (19),  sáu tấm rốm chắn (181). Ngăn tráng cũng bao gồm có hai khoang nhỏ,  bên trái là khoang chứa nước,  bên trong khoang này có phao nước (142) và một lỗ thoát nước nhỏ để nối với ống nước thải ra ngoài (102);  bên phải là khoang lò xo có lò xo (20);  ngăn giữa hai khoang là tấm ngăn cách (16A),  ba cột phun nước (122),  sáu tấm rốm chắn (182),  rơ le nhiệt độ (21). Trong đó giá đựng bát (2) được cấu tạo bởi các nan hình móc câu,  mỗi nan này được uốn thành ba đoạn sao cho có một đoạn dài và một đoạn ngắn song song với nhau,  ở giữa được nối với nhau bằng một đoạn ngắn tạo một góc khoảng 50° với đoạn ngắn nêu trên.

sentence_A: 本发明所述的胃肠内镜冲洗注射机是一种能够产生压力在胃肠内镜下注入冲洗水的装置，主要由产生压力和注水单元、控制单元和开关三部分组成。打开-关闭。该装置可调节压力和流量，以防止液体从胃肠道回流。该装置的位置适合使用。
sentence_B: ที่เก็บเศษผงขยะแบบลูกกลิ้ง ตามการประดิษฐ์ เป็นการพัฒนาให้มีประสิทธิภาพดียิ่งขึ้นแผงที่ยื่นกรีดวงรอบของขนแปรง ทำให้มีการดีดตัว เพิ่มแรงสลัดผงฝุ่น ซึ่งกล่องมีด้ามจับทำให้ใช้งานได้สะดวก และใช้เป็นที่กักเก็บผงฝุ่นขยะในตัว นอกจากนี้การที่มีด้ามจับ ทำให้สามารถออกแบบให้มีขนาดเล็กกระทัดรัด สะดวกในการใช้ตามซอกมุมอีกด้วย ตามลำดับ

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine having two ozone generating electrode plates (156,  157). Two ozone generating electrodes (156,  157) are arranged in series on the process path (152) along the blowing direction. Therefore,  air entering from the first air inlet blows along the ozone generating electrode (156) of the first plate and receives a surface discharge of the first ozone generating electrode (156) during blowing to generate ozone. Therefore,  the generated ozone-containing air enters the ozone generating electrode (157) of the second plate forward on the treatment path (152) and receives the surface discharge of the second ozone generating electrode (157) while blowing,  thereby generating additional ozone. High density ozone can be used to clean washing water.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến bộ lọc (11) dùng cho thiết bị làm sạch được bố trí trong đường cấp nước,  mà nước từ nguồn nước bên ngoài được cấp qua đó. Bộ lọc (11) gồm có hộp lọc (14),  lâi (23),  môi trường lọc (24) và tấm chặn (25). Hộp lọc (14) là chi tiết dạng bình chứa và một đầu có cửa nạp nước (15) và đầu kia có cửa xả nước (16). Lâi (23) được để trong hộp lọc (14) sao cho nằm giữa cửa nạp (15) và cửa xả (16) trong hộp lọc. Lâi (23) có thành hình trụ được tạo ra có các lỗ xuyên (23a). Môi trường lọc (24) gồm có vải may mặc được quấn thành dạng hình trụ và được giữ bởi lâi (23). Tấm chặn (25) được đỡ trên một đầu của lâi (23) và có bề mặt đối diện với hướng chảy của nước từ cửa nạp của hộp lọc (14). Sau khi nước từ cửa nạp (15) được thu nhận bởi tấm chặn (25),  bộ lọc (11) khiến cho nước tạo ra dòng chảy từ phía chu vi ngoài của môi trường lọc (24) về phía giữa để loại bỏ các tạp chất khỏi nước.

sentence_A: 本发明提出了一种锁定系统，该锁定系统提供了带多用扳手的锁定结构的轻柔操作，以及用于两侧的坐腿式运输工具。 锁定系统(30)包括锁定结构(40)和通用扳手(100)。 锁定机构(40)包括壳体(42和53)，锁定支柱(50)和闭锁门机构(6)。 多功能扳手(100)包括气缸扳手(102)和磁性扳手(110)。 气缸扳手(102)可插入转子(70)的第二锁紧凹部(74)。 在气缸扳手(102)已插入转子(70)的第二锁紧凹部(74)的状态下，磁扳手(110)可将闭锁门锁(80)的第一磁体(M1)的位置从限制位置(Q1)切换到允许位置(Q2)。 在已将气缸扳手(102)插入转子(70)的第二锁紧凹部(74)的状态下，通过使转子(70)从第一状态(P1)旋转到第二状态(P2)，将第一阻挡门(60)从第一锁紧凹部(52)被阻挡到第一锁紧凹部(52)出的打开位置(S1)。
sentence_B: การประดิษฐ์นี้เกี่ยวข้องกับกระบวนการผลิตน้ำเชื่อมโดยใช้กล้วยตากเป็นวัตถุดิบ เอ็นไซม์ถูกบ่มที่อุณหภูมิ 40-60 องศาเซลเซียส เป็นเวลา 30-180 นาที กล้วยถูกปั่นเหวี่ยง แยกหรือกรอง ไดอะตอม แล้วระเหยภายใต้แรงดันในถังนิ่งเพื่อให้ได้น้ำเชื่อมเข้มข้น

sentence_A: 油门锁定装置是公开的。当发动机在螺线管1上等待空气(真空)时，按下油门锁定开关，打开螺线管1，使空气通过空气管道吸入，拉动真空活塞，滑动油门管路。节气门管路连接在真空活塞上。按下螺线管开关2。松开锁(松开节气门)，让外部空气进入活塞(真空球)。松开螺线管3。松开阀门，让外部空气进入活塞(真空球)。当制动电流接通时。
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt bao gồm bồn giặt,  được mở hướng lên trên,  để chứa đồ giặt và nước giặt,  và bộ phận khuấy (7),  được bố trí ở phần đáy bên trong của bồn giặt,  được quay bởi bộ phận truyền động quay. Hơn nữa,  bộ phận khuấy (7) bao gồm các cánh trung tâm (27) kéo dài từ tâm quay (7a) của bộ phận khuấy (7) về phía ngoại biên (7b) của bộ phận khuấy (7),  các cánh trung tâm (27) được nhô lên từ đế (26) của bộ phận khuấy (7),  và các cánh ngoại biên (28) kéo dài từ ngoại biên (7b) về phía tâm quay (7a),  các cánh ngoại biên (28) được nhô lên từ đế (26) của bộ phận khuấy (7). Ngoài ra,  các cánh trung tâm (27) và các cánh ngoại biên (28) được bố trí ở các vị trí khác nhau theo hướng chu vi của bộ phận khuấy (7). Máy giặt do đó có thể được thực hiện,  theo đó sự không đồng đều khi giặt đồ giặt là khó xảy ra ngay cả trong trường hợp lượng nước giặt được sử dụng là nhỏ so với khối lượng đồ giặt.

sentence_A: A throttle lock device with an automobile seat pin includes a top bracket for supporting the insertion of a seat cushion nut or for supporting the insertion of a seat cushion floor,  and a side plate having a hole through a support plate. For supporting the engagement by an engagement plate connected to the base,  which is a rod or tube inserted or inserted into the top of the base,  and on the side connected to the base is an engagement plate having a hole through which the engagement plate passes. sentence_A: 本发明提供了一种X射线分析装置，用于用X射线束照射样品，所制得的X射线管具有其所产生的发散X射线束的源迹具有特征第一能量，辐射能量为正负； 第一X射线光学部分接收发散的X射线光束，并将光束朝向图案迹，同时对光束产生单色性； 以及第二X射线光学部分，接收发散的X射线光束，并将该光束朝向图案迹，同时对该光束产生单色至第二能量。 第一X射线光学部分可为来自源迹的特征能量产生单色，第二X射线光学部分可为来自源迹的制动辐射能量产生单色。 所述X射线光学部分可以是弯曲衍射光学部分，用于接收从所述X射线管发散的X射线束，并使所述光束在所述样品迹处会聚。 还进行了检测操作，以检测和测量包括玩具和电子产品在内的BAN人造产品中的各种毒素。
sentence_B: ระบบโอโซนความเข้มข้นสูงประกอบด้วยระบบผลิตน้ำโอโซนความเข้มข้นสูงปั๊ม มันเข้าไปในเครื่องซักผ้าผ่านระบบท่อของเครื่องซักผ้าเมื่อมันมาถึงขั้นตอนสุดท้ายของการล้าง เมื่อมันมาถึงขั้นตอนสุดท้ายของการล้างมันถูกควบคุมโดยตู้ควบคุม ตู้ควบคุมได้รับสัญญาณจากเครื่องซักผ้าและส่งสัญญาณไปยังเครื่องกำเนิดไฟฟ้าน้ำโอโซนความเข้มข้นสูงซึ่งจะถูกส่งไปยังเครื่องซักผ้าผ่านระบบท่อของเครื่องซักผ้า เมื่อความเข้มข้นสูงของน้ำโอโซนเข้าสู่เครื่องซักผ้าเพื่อตั้งค่าระดับน้ำเครื่องซักผ้าตู้ควบคุมสัญญาณความเข้มข้นสูงของโอโซนเครื่องกำเนิดไฟฟ้าและหยุดการป้อนข้อมูล จากนั้นตัวควบคุมเวลาที่ตั้งอยู่ในตู้ควบคุมจะเริ่มนับเวลาที่กําหนดไว้อย่างน้อย 0.1-5 นาทีซึ่งเป็นเวลาที่กําหนดไว้สําหรับน้ําโอโซนในตัวควบคุมเวลาที่เสร็จสมบูรณ์เมื่อมีเวลาอิสระท ตู้ควบคุมจะส่งสัญญาณไปยังเครื่องซักผ้าเพื่อให้เครื่องซักผ้าจะถูกลบออกจากเครื่องซักผ้าและย้ายไปยังขั้นตอนต่อไป สามารถซักผ้าที่มีคุณภาพสูงสะอาดและไม่เสียเวลาและค่าใช้จ่าย และยังช่วยปกป้องสิ่งแวดล้อม

sentence_A: The invention relates to a length adjusting mechanism of a connecting pipe assembly of a vacuum cleaner,  which comprises a guide member (4) fixedly installed at one end of an outer pipe (1),  and a sliding hole (41) is generated through the guide member (4);  The locking detail (5) can move up and down along the sliding hole (41),  and the lower end of the locking detail (5) is inserted into the locking groove (21) of the inner pipe (2) to fix the inner pipe (2) and the outer pipe (1);  The upper end of the locking member (5) is blocked by a slide (6),  which slide (6) has a groove (61) at the bottom and an inclined side (62) at the top;  The button (8) has an inclined burr (81) so that when the button (8) is pressed,  the inclined burr (81) slides on the inclined side (62) of the slide (6) to push the slide (6) to a position where the locking member (61) is aligned with the locking member (5),  so that the locking member (5) exits the locking slot (21) and enters the locking member (61),  moving the inner tube (2) along the outer tube (1).
sentence_B: เครื่องล้างถังน้ำดื่มขนาด 20 ลิตรประกอบด้วยตัวโครงหลักที่มีลักษณะเป็นรูปตัว Lด้านขวาของตัวตัวเครื่องจะเป็นส่วนขัดที่เอียงเล็กน้อย เมื่อเปิดเครื่องมอเตอร์จะหมุนทำให้มู่เลย์(Pulley) ขับ ที่ยึดกับมอเตอร์หมุนส่งดำลังไปยังมู่เลย์ (Pulley) ตาม ทำให้เพลาจานหมุนดดยมีลูกปืนตุ๊กตาเป็นตัวพยุง ส่วนขัดจะอาศัยแปรงติดสปริงที่สามารถยืดหยุ่นตามขนาดของถังเป็นตัวขัดและมีเพลาลูกกลิ้งเป็นตัวพยุงไม่ให้ถังสเตนเลส (Stainless) ส่าย ตัวขับบ่าและคอจะเป็นแขนที่ดัดโค้งติดแปรงและร้อยสปริงดันระหว่างแขนและถังสเตนเลส (Stainless) เพื่อขัดถังส่วนด้านซ้ายที่เป็นส่วนล้างนั้นจะมีทั้งปืนฉีดน้ำแรงดันสูงที่ยึดไว้กับถังรองน้ำทิ้ง สอดหัวปืนเข้ามาในกรวยรองน้ำเพื่อยิงชะล้างทำความสะอาดด้านในและด้านนอกจะเป็นท่อ (PVC) ลำเลียงน้ำจากประปาโดยตรงเข้ามายังกรวยน้ำแล้วต่อขึ้นมาเสมอกับความสูงของดครงหลักโดยจะเจาะรูเพื่อทำความสะอาดด้านนอกถัง

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine,  which comprises an operating member that performs washing of laundry,  washing of laundry and extrusion of water of laundry;  The function decay time detection unit detects the time when the function decay occurs in the operation unit;  And a controller that gradually deteriorates the function of the operation member at a time when the function of the operation member is detected to deteriorate before the function of the operation member is stopped.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt bao gồm thân máy giặt,  lồng bên trong,  và vỏ ngoài phía trên (3). Ngoài ra,  máy giặt theo sáng chế còn bao gồm panen điều khiển (8) được bố trí ở vỏ ngoài phía trên (3),  đế điều khiển (9),  vỏ bảo vệ (13) bảo vệ đế điều khiển (9),  phần chứa (5),  mà chứa vỏ bảo vệ (13) và có đáy (5a),  và bộ phận chống thấm chống thấm đế điều khiển (9). Bộ phận chống thấm có bộ phận khóa nước (17a),  và lỗ xả nước (18) được bố trí ở đáy (5a) của phần chứa (5),  và diện tích hở của lỗ xả nước (18) lớn hơn diện tích khe hở được tạo ra ở bộ phận khóa nước (17a). Do đó,  máy giặt có thể chống thấm đế điều khiển (9),  có thể ngăn sự hiển thị lỗi và sự hỏng hóc,  và có độ tin cậy tuyệt vời có thể được tạo ra.

sentence_A: A dryer based on an air dryer for a car washer,  wherein a portion of the air dryer is provided with long air guide holes facing each side of a car,  and parallel projecting material sheets are arranged along one side;  Alternatively,  a row of slots may be provided on either side of each broadcast guide slot,  and more particularly,  at one end of each sheet of material to form a certain number of strips of material. A row of connecting material sheets can be further arranged between the two side material sheets of each broadcast guide hole. The air ejected from the broadcast guide hole ejects the sheet of material rotating the same. The surface of the automobile is rapidly cleaned by beating and drying. Therefore,  time and labor are saved,  and the car washing efficiency is improved.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến thiết bị phân phối dạng ống lót ngăn kéo có thể tháo rời để phân phối chế phẩm tẩy giặt đậm đặc có thể chảy thông qua ngăn kéo của máy giặt. Sáng ché còn đề cập đến phương pháp giặt vải trong máy giặt bằng chế phẩm tẩy giặt đậm đặc và thiết bị phân phối dạng ống lót ngăn kéo,  phương pháp này bao gồm các bước :  i) chuyển chế phẩm tẩy giặt đậm đặc vào thiết bị phân phối dạng ống lót ngăn kéo,  ii) lắp thiết bị phân phối này vào ngăn kéo của máy giặt,  iii) giặt vải.

sentence_A: An opening locking device comprises two parts,  wherein one part is fixed on one side of an opening or fixed on a frame of the opening,  and an ear protrudes out of the surface of the opening or the frame. A second portion is secured to the other opening,  wherein an end of the second portion has a cartridge having an opening for engaging the lock. The padlock is a U-shaped padlock,  and is characterized in that the padlock is consistent with a box body;  and the padlock is arranged in a way that when an opened door is closed and a lock rod of the padlock is pressed,  the lock rod of the padlock is aligned with a protruding lug of a first part. The end part of the lock rod is inserted into the hook ring,  so when the hook ring is in a locked state and the hook ring is hidden in the box body,  a thief can not cut the hook ring.
sentence_B: เครื่องซักผ้าเสื่อประกอบด้วยฐานซึ่งมีถังเก็บน้ำแกนเหล็กเชื่อมกับระบบมอเตอร์มอเตอร์ควบคุมความเร็วและเลื่อนแผ่นรองผ่านหัวฉีดและระบบปั๊มเริ่มทำงานทันทีเมื่อปิดสวิตช์ . โบลเวอร์และหัวสเปรย์พร้อมหัวสเปรย์เพื่อขจัดละอองน้ำออกจากเสื่อ ล้างพรมจนสุดและม้วนขึ้นในตำแหน่งที่เก็บเสื่อ

sentence_A: A was machine includes a washing machine hold having a cylindrical shape with a sealed bottom and a parent body positioned within that main body;  The turntable is rotatably arranged on the lower part of the inner side of the washing machine holder;  The lower rotor is arranged under the turntable;  The pump chamber is generated at the inner bottom of the washing cage and comprises a lower stirrer;  The cover covers a fluid path running upward from the pump chamber along the wash cage wall and has a fluid circulation path generated thereon;  A curved channel generated at the upper part of the cover covers the fluid channel and extends toward the inner side of the washing cage,  the curved channel comprises a left channel,  a right channel and a middle channel,  the orthogonal lines of the left and right channels respectively face the inner periphery of the washing cage,  and the orthogonal lines of the middle channel face the inner side of the washing cage;  And the discharge head has an opening created in the form of a stretched opening and on the curved channel,  the opening of the discharge head extending through the left channel,  the middle channel and the right channel.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập tới cơ cấu chỉ báo trạng thái có thể điều khiển đóng mạch dùng cho thiết bị ngắt mạch không khí và thiết bị ngắt mạch không khí có cơ cấu nối này. Cơ cấu chỉ báo trạng thái có thể điều khiển đóng mạch dùng cho thiết bị ngắt mạch không khí bao gồm vi chuyển mạch lắp ở cơ cấu chuyển mạch tạo ra một lực dẫn động để chuyển mạch các bộ tiếp điểm,  vi chuyển mạch này có một tay đòn kéo dài vào cơ cấu chuyển mạch để tiếp nhận lực dẫn động,  tạo ra và đưa ra một tín hiệu điện để chỉ báo rằng thiết bị ngắt mạch không khí ở trạng thái có thể điều khiển đóng mạch,  và có một đầu cuối truyền tín hiệu để truyền tín hiệu điện tới một địa điểm cách xa,  và khớp nối bật ép tay đòn của vi chuyển mạch khiến cho vi chuyển mạch tạo ra và đưa ra tín hiệu điện chỉ khi lò xo đóng mạch để tạo ra năng lượng đàn hồi nhằm chuyển mạch các bộ tiếp điểm nạp năng lượng đàn hồi và thiết bị ngắt mạch không khí được mở.

sentence_A: 本发明涉及一种真空炊具，在用于真空炊具的盖子上安装具有真空功能和防溢流功能的盖子手柄，利用安装在所述盖子手柄处的锁紧单元将盖子锁在所述盖子上。
sentence_B: อุปกรณ์แจ้งเตือนเด็กตกค้างในรถรับส่งนักเรียนหรือรถยนต์ทั่วไปที่มีลักษณะของแผ่นรองรับการกดทับที่ติดตั้งอยู่ด้านในรถเพื่อรองรับการเหยียบหรือกดทับของเด็กที่ตกค้างภายในรถ สำหรับทำให้สวิทซ์เชื่อมต่อด้านในแผ่นรองรับการกดทับทำงานได้จากการกำหนดว่าจะให้หน้าสัมผัสของสวิทซ์เชื่อมต่อเชื่อมต่อกันหรือแยกออกจากกันเมื่อทำการล็อคประตูด้วยการล็อคของกุญแจหรือล็อคประตูด้วยสัญญาณคำสั่งแบบไร้สายจากภายนอกขณะเครื่องยนต์หยุดการทำงาน เพื่อให้สัญญาณไฟฟ้าจากแหล่งจ่ายไฟฟ้าให้อุปกรณ์แจ้งเตือนสามารถส่งผ่านไปยังหลอดแสดงผลหรือลำโพงที่ถูฏติดตั้งเข้ากับรถรับส่งนักเรียนหรือรถยนต์ทั่วไปได้

sentence_A: The invention relates to a one-way ticket IC card recovery system for a railway ticketing system. The recovery system is a recovery system that uses an IC card for one-way travel tickets (11) and uses the IC card again. A recovery system,  for example,  a card vending machine (200) provided at a departure station and equipped with a distribution assembly (202),  a distribution assembly (100) provided at the departure station and equipped with a recovery assembly (301),  and a ticketing line shielding device (300),  the recovery assembly having a ballot box (100). Generally,  a card vending machine (200) and a ticketing barricade device (300) are provided at each station. The ballot boxes for the assigned cluster and the ballot boxes for the restored cluster that have been used are public ballot boxes. The universal ballot box (100) has a screen door (101) that opens the cartridge opening portion (104) during loading and closes the cartridge opening portion during transportation.
sentence_B: เป็นการนำน้ำมันปาล์มซึ่งเป็นสารธรรมชาติมาประดิษฐ์เป็นสูตรผสมตั้งต้นในการผลิต น้ำยาล้างจาน น้ำยาทำความสะอาดพื้นผิวห้องน้ำและสุขภัณฑ์ หรือสบู่ซักผ้า แทนการใช้สารเคมี โซเดียม ลอว์ริล อีเธอร์ ซัลเฟต

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a quick release joint with a high-voltage boosting safety switch,  which is composed of a main body,  a sliding ring and a rear base. The rear base part is provided with an air through hole at the central position,  the air through hole is divided into two spaces together with the blocking part,  the blocking part is respectively provided with a plurality of through holes at both ends,  and the through holes work simultaneously. With the guide rail is a third circle of the slip ring,  which is connected between the two gaps. The male connector of the high-pressure pressurizing airtight device is locked by sliding the slip ring to open and close the air passage.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến phương pháp thu hồi kim loại quý từ thiết bị điện tử phế thải với chi phí xử lý thấp. Bằng cách nghiền thiết bị điện tử phế thải bằng máy nghiền va đập,  các thiết bị điện tử phế thải này được tách thành nền mạch in và nguyên liệu không phải nền mạch in. Sau đó,  bằng cách nghiền các nền mạch in bằng máy nghiền va đập kiểu quay,  các nền này được tách thành linh kiện đã gắn trên nền mạch in và các bộ phận không phải linh kiện. Kim loại quý được tái sinh từ các linh kiện đã tách được này.

sentence_A: 本发明所述的供水控制阀，其特征是壳体分为两个腔室，上腔室为浮阀和机械开关，下腔室为供水控制单元，有进水管和出水管。进水管随后由水泵马达和出水管进入菜地或农民的花园。
sentence_B: 制动器和/或离合器和/或加速器锁定装置是具有能够锁定制动器和/或离合器和/或加速器的特性的本发明。该锁定可用于自动和手动变速器车型。每种车型都有钢板固定转向柱，并配有固定螺栓，连接到离合器或制动器销挡住螺栓孔的位置的钢制管。连接在锁紧系统的钢杆上的钢管的一端，并有一个连接轴，以插入另一组锁紧钢板。以及可插入第一组钢管的另一组较小的钢管，其一端开口，其端部可加工用于螺栓的孔，并可抛光并焊接到用于锁定离合器销杆和或离合器销杆和或离合器销杆的钢板上。这块钢板上有一根长的手拉杆。

sentence_A: A mobile door lock system for a vehicle with a centrally controlled lock system includes a mobile door lock mounted in the vehicle to receive signals from an individual or other mobile door lock. The user must have a 4-bit code to communicate with the unlocking system with the mobile phone. The 4-bit code is uniquely programmable and the 2-bit code is used for locking and unlocking.
sentence_B: เครื่องซักผ้าขนาดเล็กแบบพกพา (portable mini-washer) ที่มีกรอบภายนอก (casing),  ถ้วยการซักล้าง และ หน้าต่างที่โปร่งใสบนกรอบภายนอก กรอบภายนอก กำหนดพื้นที่ว่างภายใน และมีหน้าด้านหน้า,  หน้าด้านข้างซ้ายในการเชื่อมต่อทางด้านข้างกับหน้าด้านหน้า,  หน้าด้านข้างขวาในการเชื่อมต่อทางด้านข้างกับหน้าด้านหน้า และ ทางด้านตรงกันข้ามกับหน้าด้านข้างซ้าย และ หน้าด้านบนในการเชื่อมต่อในแนวตั้งกับหน้าด้านหน้า,  หน้าด้านข้างซ้าย และ หน้าด้านข้างขวา ถ้วยการซักล้างรวมถึงในที่นั้นด้วยเครื่องมือทำการคน และ ส่วนที่โปร่งใสที่ซึ่งหันหน้าเข้าหาหน้าต่างที่โปร่งใสของกรอบภายนอก กรอบภายนอก และ ถ้วยการซักล้างถูกผลิตอย่างแยกจากกัน;  และ ถ้วยการซักล้างถูกวาง และ ตรึงในพื้นที่ว่างภายใน

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine provided with a water tank,  A rotating cage is arranged inside the water tank,  The edge portion of the rotary cage is made by bending the metal plate into a cylindrical shape,  Wherein such a washing machine is manufactured by performing a coating step in which an antifouling coating having an antifouling function is applied on a surface of a plate forming an outer surface of a rotating cage edge portion,  and a washing machine having an antifouling coating is applied on the outer surface of the rotating cage edge portion.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt được bố trí có vỏ ngoài;  bồn nước;  bồn quay;  phương tiện cấp nước;  phương tiện cấp được tạo kết cấu để cấp chất xử lý vải vào bồn nước;  và phương tiện điều khiển. Phương tiện điều khiển được tạo kết cấu để có thể thực hiện bước giũ,  trong đó đồ giặt được giũ trong bồn nước chứa nước và bước loại nước,  trong đó đồ giặt được loại bỏ nước bằng cách quay bồn quay ở tốc độ cao theo cả quy trình chuẩn hoặc các quy trình lưu hương,  quy trình chuẩn được thiết kế để thực hiện bước giũ và bước loại nước theo công thức định trước và quy trình lưu hương được thiết kế để thực hiện bước giũ cuối cùng của bước giũ,  được thực hiện bằng cách cấp chất xử lý vải vào bồn nước bằng phương tiện cấp,  trong khoảng thời gian dài hơn so với quy trình chuẩn.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a pickup truck end cover. Only one handle is arranged in the middle of the end cover. The user will be able to correctly lock and unlock existing locking mechanisms,  whether using an electrical system of a door center lock or using a key. Thus,  the tailgate can be closed and fully locked.
sentence_B: 根据本发明的一种带有把手的门锁装置，通过将磁极相互吸引来施加来自固定在门框一侧的部件上和固定在门框一侧的部件上的磁体2的磁力。吸力的特点是通过吸力而不是粘在吸力上，使吸力的距离更长，从而提高了设备的锁定效率，并开发了用于关闭和打开的设备，而不是内置的手柄。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine,  which includes a water tank cover installed on the upper port of the water tank surrounding the flushing tank and including a part covering the dehydration tank,  and a structure provided on the part covering the water tank cover of the flushing tank. The structure includes a water receiving portion receiving water supplied to the structure,  waterways extending from the water receiving portion in different directions so that the water received by the water receiving portion flows in corresponding directions,  and flushing ends are formed at distal ends of the waterways so that water flowing along the waterways also flows out of the flushing ends into the flushing tank.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến phương pháp dưỡng vải sợi,  phương pháp này bao gồm bước định lượng chế phẩm xử lý vải dạng rắn chứa :  (a) một hoặc nhiều chất làm mềm vải amoni bậc bốn;  và (b) hợp chất béo được chọn từ các axit béo,  rượu béo và hỗn hợp của chúng vào chu trình giặt của máy giặt tự động,  thực hiện chu trình giặt và sau đó thực hiện chu trình giũ trong máy giặt. Chế phẩm này cũng có thể được định lượng trực tiếp vào chu trình giũ. Chế phẩm theo sáng chế có thể được tạo ra dưới dạng nóng chảy đã được làm lạnh. Chế phẩm này cũng có thể chứa nước với lượng ít hơn 5% trọng lượng. Chế phẩm này còn có thể chứa một hoặc nhiều chất hoạt động bề mặt anion,  chất độn không polyme tan trong nước và các muối vô cơ không phải chất độn tan trong nước.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a fabric softening composition,  which comprises :  (a) 0.01% to 50% mass fraction of cationic or nonionic softening compounds;  (b) at least 0.001 mas percent of that water-dispersed crosslink cationic polymer is formed by polymerizing 5 to 100 mole percent of monomer with vinyl cations,  From 0% to 95% by mole of acrylamide,  And the copolyvinyl monomer crosslinking agent of 5ppm to 500ppm has two functional groups (C) of 0% to 5% of the mass of free aromatic oil,  (d) at least one cystic fabric or skin care component in the organic polymer,  the effective amount of which is present on the outside of the polymer,  the hydroxyl-oxygen functional group being attached thereto,  thereby creating an outer shell on at least a portion,  the outer shell being capable of permeating fragrance,  and the polymer having the hydroxyl-oxygen functional group not being moved into water for a long time;  And (e) the rest is water and any one or more auxiliary substances.
sentence_B: ระบบเติมอากาศโอโซนในเครื่องซักผ้าและอุปกรณ์ที่อธิบายไว้ในสิ่งประดิษฐ์ในปัจจุบันใช้ระบบการควบคุมคำสั่งเพื่อควบคุมกระบวนการซักผ้าและกระบวนการผลิตโอโซนเพื่อให้มันทำงานโดยอัตโนมัติอย่างต่อเนื่อง ประสิทธิภาพของเครื่องซักผ้าที่เพิ่มขึ้นและประสิทธิภาพของเครื่องซักผ้าจะดีขึ้นและเวลาและค่าใช้จ่ายจะลดลง ที่สำคัญที่สุดคือการรักษาน้ำในเครื่องซักผ้าแล้วรีไซเคิลจนซักเสร็จ

sentence_A: 本发明涉及一种洗衣机，包括用于容纳洗涤溶液的水桶，装在水桶内并用于容纳衣物的旋转笼，所述的容器内设有水桶和旋转笼，以及用于产生泡沫并将产生的泡沫送至所述的容器笼。 此外，该发泡器包括用于容纳从旋转泵馈送的洗涤液的发泡腔，从旋转泵馈送的洗涤液与容纳在该发泡腔中的洗涤液的溶液表面接触。 因此，能够制作出质地简单，能够有效地洗涤带有泡沫的衣物的洗衣机。
